Eligibility Criteria:

This contest is open to individuals above the age of 16 years. Participation in the contest constitutes Participant’s full and unconditional agreement to and acceptance of these Terms and Conditions (“Terms”). The term “you” refers to the “Participant”. Employees of Sponsor and its respective parent companies, affiliates, subsidiaries, advertising, promotion, fulfillment or other coordinating agencies, individuals providing services to Sponsor through an outsourcer or temporary employment agency during the contest period, and their respective immediate family members and persons living in their same household, are not eligible to participate in the competition.

Your Participation:

i. You can participate as an individual only.

ii. Teams are not allowed. The sponsor is not responsible for, and will not assist in resolving, any disputes between the participants.

iii.To participate, you must make a video of the following three steps as mentioned earlier either as a single video or split of three videos with a maximum duration of 30 mins each.

iii.You must make your own arrangements of product and equipment and cover all associated costs and expenses.

iv.You, as a Participant will be required to do the following:

The challenge is to build a creative and innovative content video using a product and utilization of its packaging. 
All participants (individual digital identity)will receive an individual code using which you will be able to upload the video(s). Incomplete entries may be disqualified.

